name: Planetary - 2º- MOON
description:
The symbology of the moon refers to the maternal function that the baby and child receives as information from those who raise them.
From that information and together with the symbolism of the sun, we can understand a little more how the child will develop throughout his life from that first information that he obtains from his environment.
That is why it is always important to combine the information of the elements, of the zodiacal qualities, the aspects and the own experience to understand the identity.
If you want to know more, buy the piece and write me to find out!

"Planetary" is the name of the result of my desire to learn and teach astrology to many people around the world, its purpose is growth, wishes and magic.
